  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will be running the 200 mile Reach The Beach Relay New Hampshire from Bretton Woods to Hampton Beach taking place 15-16 September 2017.  We are again collectively raising money for Partners In Health, to revitalize rural health clinics and train the next generation of Mexican doctors in the Sierra of Chiapas, Mexico-one of the most marginalized areas of the country, and to bring crucial surgical care to Kirehe, Rwanda.</narrative>
